  "title": "[America MNC/ No Need Exp/ Scientific Instruments] Sales Engineer @ West #HJA",
  "description": "<p>Remuneration: </p><p>Basic + 1.5% comms + AWS (NO VB) + 1100 (TA if cdd drives) + 100 HP allowance</p><p>Scope: </p><ul><li>Prospect and generate new leads</li><li>Develop and maintain relationships with existing and potential customers</li><li>Regularly conduct seminars, product demonstrations and technical presentations to customers and prospects</li><li>Develop sales proposals and negotiate contracts</li><li>Meet or exceed monthly and annual sales targets</li><li>Meet or exceed weekly sales activities targets</li><li>Collaborate with the marketing team to develop and implement effective sales strategies</li><li>Monitor industry trends and provide feedback to the sales and marketing teams</li><li>Attend trade shows and industry events to network and generate leads</li></ul><p>Requirement: </p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate Diploma/Professional Degree in Engineering (Chemical), Engineering (Environmental), Engineering (Material Science), Engineering (Environmental, Water Treatment) or equivalent.</li><li>0 - 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field</li></ul><p>TELE me at @yijingggggg or WA me at https://wa.me/+6598623556 NOW!</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to alisonchen@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Alison Chen</p><p>CEI Reg No: R25126657 </p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA Licence No.: 99C4599)</p>",
